---


<Base title="Jeremy Dubs — Video Production & Website Upgrades | Bellingham, WA">


  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Bellingham, WA — Available locally & remotely</span>
      <h1>Video Production & Website Upgrades for <em>Local Businesses</em></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">I help businesses look more professional, generate more leads, and show up better online — through polished video content and targeted website improvements.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="/work" class="btn btn--outline">View Work</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-clients">
        <span class="label">Working with</span><br />
        <span>All Star Lake Spa · Cascade Pest Control · Businesses across Western Washington</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="label">What I Do</span>
        <h2>Two services. One trusted creative partner. Both focused on <em>results.</em></h2>
        <p>Video production, editing, and website upgrades for businesses that want sharper presentation, stronger trust, and better conversions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="label">Service 01</span>
          <h3>Video Production & Editing</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">Cinematic commercials, social content, branded videos, real estate tours, and remote editing for businesses and marketing teams across the Pacific Northwest.</p>
          <div class="tags" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
            <span class="tag">Commercial video</span>
            <span class="tag">Remote editing</span>
            <span class="tag">Social reels</span>
            <span class="tag">Real estate</span>
            <span class="tag">Drone (FAA Part 107)</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn--ghost">See production services</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="label">Service 02</span>
          <h3>Website Upgrades for Local Businesses</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">I find exactly what's holding your website back and fix those specific things — without a full rebuild. Most local business sites need targeted improvements, not a $5,000 do-over.</p>
          <div class="tags" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
            <span class="tag">Homepage rewrite</span>

